originalText.text: For all those who gave this business a one star because you watched a video of a disgruntled employee attempt to threaten and extort his boss on YouTube you’re absolute morons.  Guy can’t do his job so he shows up with attitude and acting like he’s a tough guy, acts rude and condescending to his former co-workers, trespasses and then claims he was assaulted after refusing to leave private property and what does he expect to happen...roll out the red carpet and be treated like theyre old college roommates?  Give me a break.  There are proper channels to getting pay from a former employee that don’t involve threatening your past employee, trespassing and attempted character assasination.  This guy is a joke and they never should’ve hired him.  With all the shootings that take place at offices this guy was WAY OUT OF LINE.  I honestly hope that this company can get more good reviews because what this guy did and all the people who have jumped on the hate train can go to hell.  Try running a small business and then come back and talk about how easy it is to deal with employees who don’t want to do their jobs.
